import React from 'react' const GetForcastRow = (item) => { const dateString = item.ForcastDate; const timeString = dateString.split(" ")[1]; const hourMinute = timeString.split(":").slice(0, 2).join(":"); return ( {hourMinute} {item.Temperature} {item.Cloudy} {item.Wind} {item.Humaidity} {item.Pressure} ) } const GetDailyForcast = ({ item }) => { const date = new Date(item.Date); const formattedDate = date.toDateString(); return (

Forcast For {formattedDate}

{GetForcastRow(item)}
Time Temperature Cloudy Wind Humaidity Pressure
) } export default GetDailyForcast
